OL,3,CPorters strikes over 'bullying and
OL,4,Charassment' at Southampton Hospital
OL,5,Csuspended
OL,7,FSome porters at the NHS Trust which
OL,8,Fruns Southampton General Hospital were
OL,9,Fto go on strike today over claims of
OL,10,F"bullying and harassment".
OL,12,FThose strikes involving more than 60
OL,13,Fporters have been suspended following
OL,14,Fextensive talks at the conciliation
OL,15,Fservice Acas.
