OL,4,Charassment' at Southampton Hospital
OL,5,Csuspended
OL,7,FUnite the Union say the talks have
OL,8,Fmade progress on the issues affecting
OL,9,Fthe workers and as an act of good
OL,10,Ffaith, the porters' Union Unite agreed
OL,11,Fto suspend today's strike and to allow
OL,12,Ffor further talks.
OL,14,FThe Union claimed hospital porters are
OL,15,Fsubjected to restricted toilet breaks
OL,16,Fand are denied rest breaks to sit down
OL,17,Fand drink water.
