OL,7,FA Unite spokesperson said: "Following
OL,8,Flast-minute talks at Acas, Unite has
OL,9,Fagreed to suspend today's strike
OL,10,Faction.
OL,12,F"This was made as an act of good faith
OL,13,Fand to allow hospital management to
OL,14,Fresolve the outstanding issues that
OL,15,Fhave created this dispute."
